粒要4、5百鈫，唔似其他幾十鈫就買到個MICRO SD 線叉電"},{"pid":"ddea153c9ee8ef1b5b5dc9c4c5f1cb03b86969a1","tid":408724,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶到耳仔痛 太大舊<br />\n搵返B＆O講又HEA鳩我<br />\n（LV價，茶記售後）<br />\n永不再錄用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實幾易甩，絕對唔適合運動<br />\n聲算唔差但高頻、女聲，例如 SI SU 音會聽到好&quot;銀耳&quot;齒輪咁聲"},{"pid":"5233d6a51a33023758b0f40c36b4c7ee6c069a64","tid":408724,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:56:39.000Z","msg":"智post 問<br />\n有咩藍芽電量好音質ok? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3014290b0661aac49ca27eaf6d28af21eb187c84","tid":408724,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借post 問<br />\n有咩藍芽電量好音質ok? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"762d601faab5e854f23de0985a6da3c46316fd09","tid":408724,"uid":6698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帶到耳仔痛 太大舊<br />\n搵返B＆O講又HEA鳩我<br />\n（LV價，茶記售後）<br />\n永不再錄用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實幾易甩，絕對唔適合運動<br />\n聲算唔差但高頻、女聲，例如 SI SU 音會聽到好&quot;銀耳&quot;齒輪咁聲</blockquote><br />\n超易甩<br />\n帶實就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb93a0dfe0f18f708534b91d625e2e1bedabcfc","tid":408724,"uid":6698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帶到耳仔痛 太大舊<br />\n搵返B＆O講又HEA鳩我<br />\n（LV價，茶記售後）<br />\n永不再錄用</blockquote><br />\n唔同人唔同 多數要試下先架</blockquote><br />\n用開佢headphone 冇諗過咁唔舒服<br />\nlesson learnt"}]}